$\|\mathbf{q}\|^2 = \frac{25}{49}\|\mathbf{p}\|^2 = \frac{25}{49} * \frac{25}{49}\|\mathbf{v}\|^2 = \frac{25}{49}*\frac{25}{49}\|\mathbf{p}\|^2$
Now, cross multiplying $\|\mathbf{q}\|^2\|\mathbf{p}\| = \frac{25}{49}\|\mathbf{v}\|^2$ and substituting on RHS,
$\frac{\|\mathbf{q}\|^2}{\|\mathbf{q}\|\|\mathbf{p}\|} = \frac{25}{49}$
Therefore, $\frac{\|\mathbf{q}\|}{\|\mathbf{p}\|} = \frac{25}{49}$
Also, $\frac{\|\mathbf{p}\|}{\|\mathbf{v}\|} = \frac{\|\mathbf{q}\|}{\|\mathbf{v}\|}\frac{\|\mathbf{v}\|}{\|\mathbf{w}\|}$
